item.title: CVE-2024-38302|2024-08-02T04:04:25.240Z -- dell -- dell%20data%20lakehouse
item.description: Dell Data Lakehouse, version(s) 1.0.0.0, contain(s) a Missing Encryption of Sensitive Data vulnerability in the DDAE (Starburst). A low privileged attacker with adjacent network access could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to Information disclosure.
